criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1. Male or Femal with any ages;
2. The patients with the B-cell acute lymphoblast leukemia with molecular relapse after allogeneic hematopoietic stem cell transplantation with CD19 expression;
3. The estimated survival is over three months;
4. ECOG performance status of <=2 at study entry;
5. The important organs are function,such as heart and brain;
6. Understand and voluntarily sign an informed consent form.
